.TH ICONMGR "1" "February 2026" "iconmgr 202602020740-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
iconmgr \- Icon theme manager for installing and managing desktop icon themes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B iconmgr
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,COMMAND\/\fR] [\fI\,ICONTHEME\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B iconmgr
is an icon theme management system for installing, updating, and managing desktop icon themes from preconfigured GitHub repositories. It provides a unified interface for managing icon themes commonly used in Linux desktop environments.
.PP
iconmgr supports installation from the iconmgr organization repositories on GitHub, automatic icon cache updates, search functionality for discovering available icon themes, and proper icon theme version tracking. The tool is designed for desktop users who want consistent icon themes across multiple systems.
.PP
All icon themes are managed through Git repositories, making it easy to version control, update, and synchronize icon theme installations across different machines.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B makecache
Update system icon cache database after icon theme changes. This command regenerates the icon cache so newly installed icon themes become available to desktop environments and applications.
.TP
.B list
List all icon themes currently available in the iconmgr repository catalog
.TP
.B search \fI\,<term>\/\fR
Search for available icon themes matching the specified term. Useful for finding icon themes by name or style.
.TP
.B available
Show all available icon themes from the GitHub repository. Fetches complete list from GitHub API.
.TP
.B install \fI\,<icontheme>\/\fR
Install an icon theme package from the preconfigured repository. Downloads the icon theme files and installs them to the appropriate system location.
.TP
.B update \fI\,[icontheme]\/\fR
Update icon theme packages. If no icon theme is specified, updates all installed icon themes. If a specific icon theme is provided, updates only that icon theme.
.TP
.B remove \fI\,<icontheme>\/\fR
Remove an installed icon theme package and its files from the system
.TP
.B download \fI\,<icontheme>\/\fR
Download or clone an icon theme repository without installing. Useful for examining icon themes or manual installation.
.TP
.B cron \fI\,[add|remove|run]\/\fR
Manage automatic icon theme updates via cron job. Add schedules periodic updates, remove cancels scheduled updates, run executes update immediately.
.TP
.B version \fI\,<icontheme>\/\fR
Display version information for an installed icon theme package
